description: Get ready for a new standard in cushioning and comfort for you to run in with the Nike Epic React Flyknit Men’s Running Shoes. The Nike React midsole has been created following years of research to be incredibly reactive, bouncing back strongly to each and every footfall to spring you forward in your run. Despite the springiness off the foam in the midsole is extremely durable, snapping back to shape, ensuring a shoe that will still feel new after up to 300 miles of wear. Formfitting and featherweight Flyknit material through the upper wraps the foot with the snug fit of a sock to maximise comfort and stability when running. At the back of the foot a heel shelf stabilises the foot to prevent to heel from rolling back when it lands. The Epic React Flyknit outsole keeps the shoes as light as possible by placing traction in only critical spots, with rubber sections at the heel and toe enhancing running grip to drive you forward.
Formfitting and featherweight Flynkit upper wraps the foot for snug and stable fit
Flyknit upper is made from recycled plastic to reduce environmental impact of production
Nike React midsole foam is responsive, lightweight and soft. It is shaped using heatmapping of the foot to create a midsole that offer extra bounce and support in key areas
The Nike React midsole offers great bounce back snapping back from the impact of your step, time after time. Its durable construction will leave it feeling like new after up to 300 miles.
Heel shelf is placed to stabilise the back of the foot and prevent it from rocking when your foot falls
Synthetic suede lining on the heel helps prevent slippage and blisters
Traction on the outsole is optimised to cut down weight, placed only where it’s needed. Rubber sections on the toe and heel give you the grip needed to keep driving forward

title: Nike Free RN Flyknit 2018 Mens Running Shoes
breadcrumbs: Nike Free RN Flyknit 2018 Mens Running Shoes
description: A favourite of athletes who value a comfortable shoe, the Nike Free RN Flyknit 2018 has been updated to deliver an even more comfortable and adaptive fit. The Nike Free RN Flyknit 2018 Men's Running Shoes are constructed with a light an highly breathable Flyknit upper that flexes with your foot for natural movement. Breathability to the foot is further enhanced by larger holes engineered in the midfoot to keep the foot cool. Elastic yarns in the heel help to deliver a snug and adaptive fit. The fit is further enhanced in the midfoot thanks to the Flywire cables that integrate with the laces for better lock-down. An amazing underfoot feeling comes thanks to the injected Phylon core foam and IU carrier foam for a smooth ride. The auxetic tri-star pattern in the outsole and minimal sockliner work to promote a natural foot splay for a balanced and natural feel and range of motion.
1-piece Flyknit upper integrates stretch breathability and support where it is needed
Dynamic fit thanks to Flywire cables linking with laces in the midfoot and stretchy elastic yarns in the heel
Midsole utilises injected Phylon core foam and injected unit sole carrier foam for a smooth ride
Minimal sockliner mimics the curve of the foot for enhanced support
Auxetic tri-star outsole pattern adapts to your step for flexible cushioning
Texture added to toe and heel for enhanced traction

The Nike React midsole has been created following years of research to be incredibly reactive, bouncing back strongly to each and every footfall to spring you forward in your run. Despite the springiness of the foam in the midsole it is extremely durable, snapping back to shape, ensuring a shoe that will still feel new after up to 300 miles of wear. Formfitting and featherweight Flyknit material through the upper wraps the foot with the snug fit of a sock to maximise comfort and stability when running. At the back of the foot a heel shelf stabilises the foot to prevent to heel from rolling back when it lands. The Epic React Flyknit outsole keeps the shoes as light as possible by placing traction in only critical spots, with rubber sections at the heel and toe enhancing running grip to drive you forward.
Formfitting and featherweight Flynkit upper wraps the foot for snug and stable fit
Flyknit upper is made from recycled plastic to reduce environmental impact of production
Nike React midsole foam is responsive, lightweight and soft. It is shaped using heatmapping of the foot to create a midsole that offers extra bounce and support in key areas
The Nike React midsole offers great bounce back snapping back from the impact of your step, time after time. Its durable construction will leave it feeling like new after up to 300 miles.
Heel shelf is placed to stabilise the back of the foot and prevent it from rocking when your foot falls
Synthetic suede lining on the heel helps prevent slippage and blisters
Traction on the outsole is optimised to cut down weight, placed only where it’s needed. Rubber sections on the toe and heel give you the grip needed to keep driving forward

title: Nike Mercurial Superfly 6 Academy MG Kids Football Boots
breadcrumbs: Nike Mercurial Superfly 6 Academy MG Kids Football Boots
description: They’ll be ready to launch into their top speed from the get-go in the Nike Mercurial Superfly 6 Academy MG Kid’s Football Boots. Designed to support young players who prioritise speed, they are built from top down to provide a close and supportive fit to the foot. The Dynamic Fit collar connects the 2-tone synthetic upper to the lower leg while leaving the ankle with full mobility. Screenprinted micro-texture throughout the upper delivers grip and control on the ball, helping them to control the ball during running play. The internal lining and textile heel lining help grip the foot in place reducing movement within the boot. Podular plates in the heel and forefoot of the outsole deliver propulsive traction for acceleration. Chevron and hollow-point conical studs are designed to deliver the grip needed to play on both natural and artificial grass surfaces making it a perfect boot for your football fanatic regardless of where they play.

title: Nike Mercurial Vapor XII Mens Football Boots

description: Leave the defence choking on your dust trail, in the Nike Mercurial Superfly VI Elite Men’s Football Boots. title: Nike Epic React Flyknit Womens Running Shoes
breadcrumbs: Nike Epic React Flyknit Womens Running Shoes
description: Get ready for a new standard in cushioning and comfort, for you to run in with the Nike Epic React Flyknit Men’s Running Shoes. The Nike React midsole has been created following years of research to be incredibly reactive, bouncing back strongly to each and every footfall to spring you forward in your run. Despite the springiness of the foam in the midsole it is extremely durable, snapping back to shape, ensuring a shoe that will still feel new after up to 300 miles of wear. Formfitting and featherweight Flyknit material through the upper wraps the foot with the snug fit of a sock to maximise comfort and stability when running. At the back of the foot, a heel shelf stabilises the foot to prevent to heel from rolling back when it lands. The Epic React Flyknit outsole keeps the shoes as light as possible by placing traction in only critical spots, with rubber sections at the heel and toe enhancing running grip to drive you forward.
Formfitting and featherweight Flynkit upper wraps the foot for a snug and stable fit
Flyknit upper is made from recycled plastic to reduce environmental impact of production
Nike React midsole foam is responsive, lightweight and soft. It is shaped using heatmapping of the foot to create a midsole that offers extra bounce and support in key areas

breadcrumbs: Nike Epic React Flyknit Kids Running Shoes
description: Get  your youngster ready to fly on a new standard of cushioning in the Nike Epic React Flyknit Kid’s Running Shoes. The Nike React midsole has been engineered to deliver incredibly reactive bounce back to each and every footfall springing your super speedster through their run. The foam in the midsole is extremely durable, snapping back to shape, ensuring a fresh feel  after up to hundreds of miles of wear. Formfitting and featherweight Flyknit material through the upper wraps the foot with the snug fit of a sock to maximise comfort and stability when running. At the back of the foot a heel shelf stabilises the foot preventing the heel from rolling back when it lands. The Epic React Flyknit outsole keeps the shoes as light as possible by placing traction in only critical spots, with rubber sections at the heel and toe enhancing running grip to keep up with your kid's endless energy and active lifestyle.

description: Inspired by dynamic players at the top of the game, the Nike Mercurial Superflyx VI Elite Men’s Indoor Soccer Shoes are made for speedy players who like to dictate the pace of play.
